"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"üê• GM web3 hatchlings!! Today we will be covering[ Coinbase](https://help.coinbase.com/en/coinbase/getting-started/crypto-education/what-is-coinbase), and how to buy & sell your first Bitcoin (BTC) and Ethereum (ETH) on the platform!!\\n\\nIt can be a bit daunting, but fear not! üêá Follow our bushy tail and we shall guide you down the rabbit hole!\\n\\nFirst be sure to check out Coinbase‚Äôs articles on what Ethereum and Bitcoin are!\\n\\n* [What is Bitcoin?](https://www.coinbase.com/learn/crypto-basics/what-is-bitcoin)\\n* [What is Ethereum?](https://www.coinbase.com/learn/crypto-basics/what-is-ethereum)\\n\\n### I am ready! What is Coinbase?\\n\\n[Coinbase](https://help.coinbase.com/en/coinbase/getting-started/crypto-education/what-is-coinbase) is an online exchange platform that lets you buy and sell various cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin & Ethereum from fiat (like USD, EUR) currencies. Coinbase is amazing because it exists as an exchange between traditional finance like banks and the crypto currency world! Decentralized Exchanges (DEXs) only let you exchange between crypto currencies, but Centralized Exchanges (CEXs) like Coinbase lets us exchange our fiat into crypto we can use or hold, and back into fiat. üéà\\n\\nü§ø Now let us dive into how we can buy our first crypto!\\n\\nFirst things first, you are going to want to set up a Coinbase account. Click **Get Started** on their [homepage](https://www.coinbase.com/), and visit their help guide [here](https://help.coinbase.com/en/coinbase/getting-started/getting-started-with-coinbase/create-a-coinbase-account) for a step by step.\\n\\n## üåü How to Buy Bitcoin (BTC) and Ethereum (ETH)\\n\\nüíÉ Once you have created your account and signed in, you are ready to buy BTC or ETH!\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FDOd4xapFDx1dZLq2HxpmS.png&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n1. Click **Buy/Sell** in the top right corner.\\n2. A menu will open asking how much Bitcoin you would like to buy! Enter the amount you would like to exchange, and select your payment method.\\n3. Once you have entered how much you would like to exchange, click **Preview Buy** to see your order preview.\\n   1. ***Note***: *Coinbase and most other exchanges take a small fee for using their platform to buy/sell*\\n4. The Order preview shows how much crypto (BTC) you will be receiving, the price of the BTC at the purchase, Coinbase fee, payment method, and total.\\n5. Confirm by clicking **Buy now**.\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FCXCm3ch5-tiXOT0vzlVpl.png&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n**ü•≥ And that‚Äôs it!! You have officially exchanged fiat for your first crypto currency!!**\\n\\nTo buy Ethereum (ETH) and the other crypto currencies offered on the exchange:\\n\\n1. Go back to the **Buy/Sell** menu, and click the toggle next to Bitcoin.\\n2. It will open a menu that will let you select a cryptocurrency, let‚Äôs click ETH for now.\\n3. Enter the amount you would like to exchange, click **Preview Buy**,\\n4. Click **Buy now** to confirm.\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FJT8AgpAcRrO4rdI-7wCeo.png&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\nüå± **Congratulations! You bought your first BTC and ETH!! Welcome to crypto!!**\\n\\n## üíé How to Sell Bitcoin (BTC) and Ethereum (ETH)\\n\\nNow that you own some crypto, it‚Äôs time to look at how you would sell BTC and ETH.\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FDOd4xapFDx1dZLq2HxpmS.png&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n1. Click on **Buy/Sell** to open the menu, and click on the Sell tab\\n2. Enter how much BTC you would like to sell\\n   1. ***Note***: *Hitting the arrow on the right side changes whether you want to enter your sale in fiat amount or crypto. The sale processes are the same, it‚Äôs just how you want to enter the amount.*\\n3. Click **Sell Bitcoin** to open the Order preview where you can see your Total payout\\n4. Click **Sell now** to confirm!\\n\\n![](https://mirror.xyz/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.mirror-media.xyz%2Fpublication-images%2FRT68PB_uXiuXPAAPW2H91.png&w=3840&q=90)\\n\\n### ü§© To sell ETH or other crypto, the process is the same!\\n\\n1. Just click the toggle next to bitcoin to view the other cryptocurrencies you hold, and click ETH.\\n2. Enter the amount you would like to sell, and click **Sell Ethereum** to open the order preview and view your Total payout.\\n3. Click **Sell now** to confirm!\\n\\n**üòé That‚Äôs it!**\\n\\nYou can now use your exchanged fiat to buy more crypto, or transfer it to your bank.\\n\\nThat‚Äôs all for today! I hope you enjoyed this little guide down the rabbithole. üêáüï≥\\n\\nPlease be sure to check out our Mirror articles and follow us on Twitter for all things crypto and web3.\\n\\n[https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/](https://rabbithole.mirror.xyz/)\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/rabbithole_gg](https://twitter.com/rabbithole_gg)\\n\\nüíï Stay curious frens!\",\"timestamp\":1639166916,\"title\":\"Tutorial: How to Buy and Sell BTC/ETH on Coinbase\",\"publication\":\"rabbithole\"},\"digest\":\"TP-MaRFooe_QrTIrdIn5RV9AlJ5fyRJTRfu7NZleVok\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x75A548a2Df9Ba12af496BD5364F642C9cE3C3976\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"NFrv_dqj145jHbm_AqNs1yf5wN1V1FKpNpg9NCWYSWo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IC7mQ0yXBzb3CCkff0PXoS6j4TIh0YHkw-dWcDUFgVw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"wLjLEYo67cCpDarwO4iSnPr6VInkoWbRAFbWUgTDH7qBwlM2t7aEcUS9g1LoVMLTDt-S5lwIo6eaiioF8MVdrQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x652ed32b71af48cb1a4618ca363efd5c7775286b54e8b63ce1a8c21208f8e7d22cdda748c6b452413aa9e5526e583dc6cf739cb2544d6a8eb530649d10c98f031b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize the publication of articles on rabbithole.mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"NFrv_dqj145jHbm_AqNs1yf5wN1V1FKpNpg9NCWYSWo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"IC7mQ0yXBzb3CCkff0PXoS6j4TIh0YHkw-dWcDUFgVw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"U26L_PpG4FC_Jy1bscs_-IVw_iRUAnG9yas_WD0Q8Mc\"}"